---
description: Frontend engineering standards
alwaysApply: true
---

Always follow React best practices.

Use reusable components.

Never duplicate UI.

Never hardcode colors.

Always use design tokens.

Never fetch APIs directly inside components.

Use services and hooks.

Prefer composition over inheritance.

Keep components under approximately 200 lines.

Support loading, empty and error states.

Accessibility is required.

Prefer skeletons over loading spinners.
